The perfect age is now – introducing the new Age Perfect Collagen Expert Day Cream with Gillian Anderson. Embrace replenishing mature skin just like @gilliana, reveal smoother, firmer skin.

Ride along with @caradelevingne and the new, improved Color Vive range for vibrant, protected hair.

Photographer: @ethanjamesgreen
Hair Stylist: @stephanelancien
Makeup: @harold_james

#LOrealParis #LOrealParisHaircare #ColorVive

L'Oréal Paris is leveraging packaging science by optimizing plastic use. Discover our new recyclable pouches for 60% less plastic with our new Elvive Color Vive refills. Bisous from Pompidou!

caption.text:
Too often, women end up blaming themselves for being harassed. 
Street harassment is NEVER your fault.

Nothing should stand between a woman and her self-worth.

Everyone can be part of the solution. Take a Stand and get trained on how to fight against street harassment with @lorealparis and @righttobeorg.

To get trained, check the link in bio. 

#LOrealParis #WeStandUp #WorthIt #WomenEmpowerment  #StopStreetHarassment

Whatever the clothes, shoes or make-up you wear, street harassment is NEVER your fault. Nothing should stand between a woman and her self-worth.

Learn how to fight against street harassment with the Stand Up training program by @lorealparis.
To get trained, check the link in bio. 

#WeStandUp #LOrealParis #WorthIt 
#WomenEmpowerment #StopStreetHarassment

caption.text:
Did you know that 1 out of 2 people think that women are sometimes responsible for situations of sexual harassment in public spaces due to their attitudes or appearance? This is the result of a recent L’Oréal Paris study conducted with Ipsos in 20 countries*.

It’s time to shift the mindset on sexual harassment in public places. Join @lorealparis and @righttobeorg in the fight against street harassment.

Take the Stand Up training and learn how to react when facing it.
